    "spell_type": "spell",
    "subtype": "spell",
    "text": "You sense a spiritual resonance of deep anguish in the earth beneath your feet, the walls surrounding you, or the fragments of souls left behind in a place of calamity. You draw on this reservoir of pain and unleash its force against your enemies, dealing 8d8 spirit damage. On a critical failure, the creature is also stunned for 1 round as it reels from the impact of so much anguish.",
